    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per MRL 2 scoping, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application context described in the bound Requirement (https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) and Claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis). No critical weakeners identified.",
